    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example utilizes a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission delivering power to the rear wheels via a factory variable M-differential lock. Performance is maintained through documented preventative maintenance, including a Vanos system refresh and structural subframe reinforcement. The chassis retains its sharp turn-in characteristics thanks to refreshed bushings and a well-sorted MacPherson/multi-link suspension geometry. A purist-spec driver with excellent compression and linear power delivery across the entire rev range.",
