    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers a perfect balance of luxury and performance. The exterior is finished in a striking Deep Cobalt Metallic that still retains a high-gloss luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway driving. The body panels are perfectly aligned with no dings or dents to speak of. Inside, you'll find a spacious cabin appointed in supple Parchment leather. The upholstery is in excellent shape, showing only slight softening on the driver's side bolster. All onboard technology, including the premium surround-sound system and dual-zone climate control, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and has been serviced at regular intervals; we recently completed a full oil service and brake inspection. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring a quiet and confident ride for the next owner. This is a solid, reliable vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next chapter.",
